opennlp.ccg.disjunctivizer
Class LabelMatchFilter

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.disjunctivizer.LabelMatchFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Filter<LFEdge>
public class LabelMatchFilter
extends Object
implements Filter<LFEdge>

A filter for edges based on a comparison of their labels. Instances of this class compare a specified basis edge label, so that the allows(LFEdge) method returns true if it is equivalent to the specified edge's label.

Author:
Scott Martin
